" pasfhocail a sheoladh trí ríomhphost. Rinneadh an chéad tiomantas ar"

#: ../../../app/views/pages/about.html.erb:27
msgid "The public service at pwpush.com went live shortly after."
msgstr "Chuaigh an tseirbhís phoiblí ag pwpush.com beo go gairid ina dhiaidh sin."

#: ../../../app/views/pages/about.html.erb:30
msgid ""
"Over the years it grew into a full-featured application—passwords, URLs, file "
"uploads, QR codes, a JSON API, dozens of languages, and a large self-hosted co"
"mmunity. Today it is used by companies, teams, and individuals who want a simp"
"le, auditable way to share secrets without leaving them in inboxes or messagin"
"g apps."
msgstr ""
"Le himeacht ama, d’fhás sé ina fheidhmchlár lánghnéitheach—pasfhocail, URLanna"
", uaslódálacha comhad, cóid QR, API JSON, mórán teangacha, agus pobal mór féin"
"óstáilte. Sa lá atá inniu ann, úsáideann cuideachtaí, foirne agus daoine aonai"
"r é ar mian leo bealach simplí, iniúchta a bheith acu chun rúin a roinnt gan i"
"ad a fhágáil i mboscaí isteach ná in aipeanna teachtaireachtaí."

#: ../../../app/views/pages/about.html.erb:33
msgid "In 2024,"
msgstr "Sa bhliain 2024,"

#: ../../../app/views/pages/about.html.erb:35
