msgid "Learn More"
msgstr "Foghlaim Tuilleadh"

#: ../../../app/views/pages/generate_key.html.erb:143
msgid "For detailed configuration options and deployment strategies, see the"
msgstr ""
"Le haghaidh roghanna cumraíochta mionsonraithe agus straitéisí imscartha, féac"
