msgstr "Criptithe & neamhbhuan"

#: ../../../app/views/users/first_runs/new.html.erb:144
msgid ""
"Secrets are stored encrypted and removed automatically after they expire or ar"
"e viewed."
msgstr ""
"Stóráiltear rúin criptithe agus baintear iad go huathoibríoch tar éis dóibh du"
"l in éag nó tar éis a bhfeictear iad."

#: ../../../app/views/users/first_runs/new.html.erb:152
msgid "Passwords, text & files"
